import { black } from './colors'

const baseFontColor = black
const baseFontFamily = "'neuzeit-grotesk', 'helvetics', 'arial', sans-serif"
const rootFontSize = 14
const rootFontSizePx = `${rootFontSize}px`

export {
  baseFontColor,
  baseFontFamily,
  rootFontSize,
  rootFontSizePx,
}
